Paint-IO

Create with friends!

What is it?

Paint-IO is an online paint app. Along with being able to save your artwork, you can also have your friends join and draw together on the same canvas!

How did we make it?

This app was built using:

  • Node
  • Express
  • MongoDB
  • React
  • Socket.IO

How do I use it?

I want to just draw

Click on the color you want, choose a brush size and just start drawing!

I want to erase and start over

Click on the "Clear Canvas" button and you'll have another blank canvas to create something new!

I want to save my masterpiece

Once you're done making beautiful art, just click "Save Canvas" and it will be posted to the Gallery for everyone to enjoy!

I want to draw with my friends

To join a shared drawing space, just enter the room ID and click "Join Room". Don't have a room ID yet? Make one up and share it with your friends! We recommend something around 6 random characters.

I accidentally typed the room ID incorrectly

No problem, just click "Leave Room" and try again.
